cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely sub-category as the paper focuses on image classification and uses deep learning models for predicting the category path. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also likely as the paper deals with organizing and categorizing large-scale product catalogs. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible sub-category as the paper uses deep learning models for classification. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a possible sub-category as the paper uses Attention based Sequence models for predicting the category path. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible sub-category as the paper deals with a large dataset of clothing product images.
